{{Quote|The Fiend of Earth, who drains and decays the soil itself.|Description}}
'''Lich''' is the [[Four Fiends (Final Fantasy)|Fiend of Earth]] from the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. He appears at the bottom of the [[Cavern of Earth]]. He is [[undead]] with the appearance of a skeleton.

