==Behind the scenes==
Lich is the only Chaos Fiend who does not talk to the party before fighting them. The same occurs when it reappears in ''[[Final Fantasy IV: The After Years]]''. In subsequent releases, the Lich does talk to the party.

Lich makes a major appearance in the ''Final Fantasy'' parody webcomic ''[[8-Bit Theater]]'', where he is one of the Four Fiends and guards the Earth Orb from the Light Warriors.

Due to a bug in the PSP version, if the game crashes while in the Lich fight, more Liches may spawn. This may also happen if ''Final Fantasy'' is closed during the Lich fight. This can cause problems with leaving the cave.

